data.meta_description: Bela IV OF HUNGARY was born on November 29, 1206, son of Andrew II OF HUNGARY and Gertrude OF MERANIA. He was married in the year 1218 to Maria LASKARINA, they had 4 children. He died on May  3, 1270 in Margiteiland, Budapest, Hungary. This information is part of Family tree Riny Doyle geboren Marinus van Waard by Riny Doyle on Genealogy Online.
